reviewText: I received 2 copies of this DVD-R and none of them played. Be aware of these non original DVD.

Wade Radford and Jason Impey are at it again! Boys Behind Bars 3 is here, and is perhaps the best of the lot. While many franchises sputter and die out, BBB is, if anything, only gaining strength Darrell and Mizz Muncher are back, and after Darrell takes a group leader hostage, he and the others set about torturing her and one another it's a tense, and bloody good time, definitely not for the squeamish or easily offended.
